This is the error that I get : Runtime error (MissingMethodException): Method not found: 'Void Microsoft.Scripting.Utils.ExceptionUtils.RemoveData(System.Exception, System.Object)'. Traceback:

line 12, in <module>, "C:\Program Files\Rhino WIP\Plug-ins\IronPython\Lib\ntpath.py"
